headline: 2 Reasons to Watch HSY and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Hershey trades at $165.35 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 11.1% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 7.3%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
